### Git Workflow

**IMPORTANT**: Never `git push` without explicit user approval (per user rules).

```bash
# Check status
git status

# Stage changes
git add <files>

# Commit (only when user explicitly requests)
git commit -m "message"

# DO NOT run git push without asking user first!
```
